latestIgtvVideos.title: Ardor One Step Dryer & Volumizer Review
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I recently purchased a Dupe of Revlon One-Step Hair Dryer. The Revlon brush leaves you with Shiny, bouncy locks in a fraction of the time it would take with other tools. Unfortunately at AED 388, it not be within budget for many who are looking to achieve the same result.
Luckily I came across this Ardor HairDryer Brush at @thebeautycorp.uae which is an affordable alternative and is an “exact” replacement for the Revlon brush
Check the video of How to use the brush and I would 100% recommend this tool to your styling kit. This Hair dryer brush cuts my time to half and isn’t that heavy too.
🔸MY TAKE - If you are looking for an affordable, easy, and quick way to style your hair at home the Ardor One step Dryer and Volumizer  is a top Contender for a simple styling tool!
Lemme know what you think about this tool and if you would buy the same!!
.

We finally did it.
After years of “next time” and “let’s plan soon” — we cousins went back to the beach that made our childhood magical.
This time, with our kids.
Same place, same chaos, double the memories.

If you’ve been thinking of planning something like this…
This is your sign.
Do it. Go back. Take your people with you.
You won’t regret it.
